==Galician==
{{was fwotd|gl|2019|April|24}}
===Etymology===
{{unk|gl|title=Obscure}}; perhaps from {{m|gl||*enxamardo}}, from {{affix|gl|enxame|t1=swarm|-ardo|nocat=1}}, or a derivation of {{m|gl|xebrar|t=to separate}}. Alternatively from {{der|gl|qfa-sub-ibe}}. Compare {{cog|es|jabardo|t=swarm}} and the dialectal {{cog|pt|javardo|t=boar}}, which is probably unrelated.<ref>{{R:es:DCECH|jabardo}}</ref>
